snippet.title: Vangaro Tactics - Demo Out Now
snippet.description:
Play the Demo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2221530/Vangaro_Tactics/

Vangaro Tactics is an upcoming colorful turn-based strategy game with unique commanders and Stealth Missions.
Game developer: @niadocraz 
Trailer music by @SergisPiano 

Website: http://vangarotactics.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/niadocraz
